txt.en: Asilimu has asked you to gather ichor and silk from the spiders in Ushbarab.
Bring the spider ichor and spider silk back to Asilimu near Ushbarab

'Ah, you have returned! And with the silks and ichor, no less.\n\n'Your courage has spared me from those beasts and ensured the wellbeing of those in need. I thank you, [placeholder]. Be safe on your travels.'
Asilimu has asked for your help gathering ichor and silk from nearby spiders in Ushbarab.

'A welcomed sight you are, [placeholder]!

'I have been working to make remedies for the people in need here in Urash DÃ¢r, but I find myself at an impasse. The ingredients that I need to replenish are spider silks and ichor. I must confess that I myself am dreadfully afraid of those monsters.

'Might you gather the supplies I need? You can find all that I need nearby in Ushbarab. Your efforts will not go unrewarded, and it will be a great help to people in need.'
